casebody.data:
Michael SWAIN, petitioner,
v.
FLORIDA. No. 12-10196. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013.

Case below, 117 So.3d 424.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
